!TO AND OWNERSHIP OF THE SOFTWARE IS HEREBY TRANSFERRED.
!
!THE INFORMATION IN THIS SOFTWARE IS SUBJECT TO CHANGE WITHOUT NOTICE AND 
!SHOULD NOT BE CONSTRUED AS A COMMITMENT BY DIGITAL EQUIPMENT CORPORATION.
